            <lg xml:id="TK1040">
<l>ilameṉ ṟacaii yiruppāraik kāṇi </l>
<l>ṉilameṉṉu nallā ṇakum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The maiden, Earth, will laugh at the sight of those who plead poverty and lead an idle life.</l>
